---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import profilePic from "../images/profile.jpeg";
const pageTitle = "Welcome";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="my-12 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-neutral-800 text-4xl text-center">Hi, I'm Will 🦆</h1>
    <h2 class="text-teal-600 text-2xl text-center italic mt-2">
      and this is my website
    </h2>
  </div>
  <Image
    class="my-12 mx-auto"
    src={profilePic}
    alt="Will and his wife Nancy sitting at a coffee shop."
    width="600"
    loading="eager"
  />
  <div class="my-12 mx-auto">
    <h3 class="text-teal-600 text-xl mt-6 mb-2">About Me</h3>
    <p>
      I've been a professional church musician for the past ten years. Now, I'm
      learning how to program as I seek a career in full-stack web development!
      I'm married to the beautiful and talented Nancy, and the Lord has blessed
      us with two wonderful boys named Oliver and Sullivan.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-teal-600 text-xl mt-6 mb-2">What I'm Learning</h3>
    <p>
      Ever since being introduced to the world of computer science and
      programming, I've been spending most of my free time learning and building
      cool things. Beyond the standard web development stuff, I'm also
      interested in learning more about systems programming and low-level
      languages like C.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-teal-600 text-xl mt-6 mb-2">What's up with the 🦆?</h3>
    <p>
      Ducks are cool little guys. Some might even call them <em>majestic.</em> I
      enjoy watching ducks, feeding ducks, and collecting duck memorabilia. There
      are worse hobbies.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
